{{ZScriptNote}}
bool '''CanRaise''' ()
==Usage== Performs a check on the calling actor to see if it can be resurrected. The actor cannot be resurrected if: *it is not a {{Flag|CORPSE|corpse}}. *the duration of its current state is not -1 and said state lacks the {{c|[[Actor_states#CanRaise|CanRaise]]}} keyword. *it is a player. *lacks the {{c|Raise}} state. *there is not enough room for it to raise.
===Return value=== The function returns ''true'' if the actor can be resurrected, otherwise it returns ''false''.
